{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_52_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 一人で十分、旅行を楽しめますので",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— Night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのワイン、美味しかったわね……\nもう少し飲みたいけど、この近くのお店にはあるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The wine earlier was delicious…\nI’d like to have a bit more. I wonder if any places nearby have it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2333333691,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6066.6668893,
          "startTime": 7.9333333691
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4893877069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ……mihoさん\nもう夜ですけど、これから出かけるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… miho-san?\nIt’s already night—are you heading out now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、みんなも旅館に戻ってきて\nこれから部屋で女子会だって盛り上がってましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone just got back to the ryokan‚\nand they were getting excited about having a girls’ night in their room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6562143683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "それが嫌だから、外で食事をしようと思って\n今、良さそうなお店を探してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly why I decided to eat out instead‚\nand I’m looking for a decent place right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1857607882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーの中で、ずっと遙子に絡まれてたんですから\n自由時間くらい、好きにさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko kept bothering me the whole time in the taxi.\nAt least let me do what I want during my free time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それだけmihoさんを頼りにしてるんですよ……\nそれで、いい店はありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that just means everyone relies on you that much…\nSo‚ did you find a good place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4333349586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9979149223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。まぁ。……昼間に、ワイナリーに行ったんですが\nその時にいただいたワインをもう少し飲みたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. More or less… I went to a winery earlier today‚\nand I wanted to drink a bit more of the wine I had there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8333349586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "この近辺で、扱っているお店を探して……って\nなんですか。人を飲んだくれのように見て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was looking for a nearby place that has it…\nWhat is it? You’re looking at me like I’m some kind of drunk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6877563518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり山梨くんだりまで連れて来られたので\nせめて名産品を味わって帰ろうと思っただけですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was suddenly dragged all the way out to Yamanashi‚\nso I figured I might as well enjoy some local specialties before heading back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "それにワインを飲むだけではなくて\n一応、ちゃんと山梨の観光もしてきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it’s not like I only drank wine.\nI did properly do some sightseeing around Yamanashi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7666682919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.4195252778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "戦国武将の城館跡に行ってきましたが\n併設の宝物殿はなかなか興味深かったですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I visited the ruins of a Sengoku-era warlord’s residence‚\nand the on-site treasure museum was quite interesting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、武田信玄！\nやっぱり名字が同じだと、気になるものなんですかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Takeda Shingen!\nI guess sharing the same surname makes it catch your attention‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6541059218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "最近、たまたまそういう小説を読んだだけです\n安直な発想はいかがなものかと思いますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just happened to read a novel like that recently.\nI’d say that’s a rather simplistic assumption.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4333349586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5701831542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……まぁ、旅行でずっと一人も味気ないでしょう\n俺で良ければ、飲み屋にお付き合いしますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… well‚ being alone the whole trip would feel a bit dull‚ wouldn’t it?\nIf you don’t mind‚ I could keep you company at a bar…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4666682919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3191395803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "結構です。いちいちお気遣いいただかなくても\n一人で十分、旅行を楽しめますので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ thank you. There’s no need for you to fuss over me.\nI can enjoy this trip on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "それに貴方だって、私の相手をしているよりは\n遙子や他の誰かと一緒の方が、楽しいでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ you’d probably have more fun spending time\nwith Haruko or someone else than keeping me company.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.405352724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、失礼します\n{user}さんも、他の子達といい夜を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ I’ll be going.\nHave a nice evening with the others too‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7000016253,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3961.3155679000015,
          "startTime": 113.3666682919
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.9670310064
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.9670310064
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 116.2170310064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんはああ言ったけど）\n（まさか、女子会に俺が紛れ込む訳にはいかないし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That’s what miho-san said‚ but…）\n（There’s no way I could just join in on a girls’ night.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4281420752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（今日くらい、ちょっと飲んでもいいよな）\n（一人でゆっくりする時間も、最近は少なかったし……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It should be fine to have a few drinks tonight.）\n（I haven’t had much time to relax alone lately…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.6602962855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、一人なんですが、まだ空いている席は……\n…………え、{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ I’m by myself—do you still have an open seat…\n…Eh‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1666682919,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 173.03867309999532,
          "startTime": 130.8333349586
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　奇遇ですね\nmihoさんが探してた店も、まさかここだったとは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? What a coincidence.\nI didn’t expect the place you were looking for to be here too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.171271392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "……さっき調べたお店に行ったら、満席だったので\nこちらのお店にもワインがあると聞いて来たんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The place I checked earlier was full‚\nso I came here after hearing they also serve the wine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9000016253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_52_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "まさか貴方が羽を伸ばしているとは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never imagined I’d find you here‚ taking it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
